{"tid":1543333,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［緊急］留台香港學生請入！！台灣人以為我地贏左啊！","createTime":"2019-09-05T06:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:00:59.000Z","uid":145664,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"19d472871ea25a95b982358325323b3164ada7b9","tid":1543333,"uid":145664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T06:53:40.000Z","msg":"我有個跟得香港新聞好貼既台灣朋友同我講<br />\nPtt同dcard上面都一堆人以為我地贏左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1HAknKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1HAknKz.jpg&h=f2a39d7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCq4PpA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUCq4PpA.jpg&h=7d8d9ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJcZDhV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJcZDhV.jpg&h=ac077ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我朋友已經幫手係上面澄清緊<br />\n奈可我冇ac 幫唔到手<br />\n又暫時未有登報澄清行動（我諗後生個輩都唔睇）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以係時候靠係台灣讀書既你幫幫手發動文宣！！！<br />\n解釋比台灣人聽 我地仲未贏架！！<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>文宣可以參考呢幾個post：</strong><br />\n<br />\n終於撒回 大家休息下啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538262</a><br />\n[引誓］香港人，入黎發誓，五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538055</a><br />\n《致香港人及林鄭月娥：讓我們回到一切之前》<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1541288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1541288</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>文宣圖</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eRCVV6D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeRCVV6D.png&h=da8b2e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qasyHME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqasyHME.jpg&h=e4cdb5cf&s={SIZ